name: BukitJangkrik Natural Water Swim
address: Jl. Bukit Jangkrik, Samplangan, Kec. Gianyar, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80515, Indonesia
review 1: Amazing natural swimming"pool". Big, about 2 meters deep. Sorrounded by Rice field, jungle, a Temple and small Bales to relax in. The water felt fresh and clean, had some fish in it!
review 2:
Natural Water Swim is a tourist spot located in Bukit Jangkrik Village and has a cool climate, perfect for spending weekends with family or friends.

The existence of Subak temple, shady trees, small lakes, fishing areas and even swimming area is guaranteed to be able to relieve all tiredness.

For those who like photography, this place has good photo spots, often also used as a place for couples who will do a pre-wedding photo session.
